    Hero

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EnhancedHuman
    An "enhanced" human is born as a mere mortal (e.g., Billy Batson) but later gains the ability to turn into a superhero (e.g., Captain Marvel) through some magical or science fiction plot device (e.g., by saying the name of the wizard "Shazam").
    Human
    Some mere mortals are nonetheless "super" heroes thanks to their fearlessness and training.
    SecretAgent
    A secret agent has both a name and an alias, usually a number.
    SuperHero  
    SuperHuman
    A superhuman is born with "powers and abilities far beyond those of mortal men" (e.g., the Amazonian Wonder Woman) but usually adopts a mild-mannered secret identity (e.g., "Diana Prince").
